---
// CoverageMap.astro — Sección de cobertura con mapa embebido
---

<section class="coverage section bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="coverage__grid">
      <div class="coverage__info reveal">
        <h2>Cobertura en toda la <span>Región de O'Higgins</span></h2>
        <p>Operamos desde Rancagua con cobertura en toda la VI Región. Llegamos a tu hogar, comercio o industria con instalación rápida y monitoreo 24/7.</p>
        <ul class="coverage__list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Rancagua y Machalí (Radio Urbano y Periferia)</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Graneros, Codegua, Mostazal</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Requínoa, Rengo, San Vicente</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> San Fernando, Chimbarongo, Nancagua</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Santa Cruz, Palmilla, Peralillo</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Pichilemu, Navidad, Lago Rapel</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Doñihue, Olivar, Coltauco</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/#contacto" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
          Agenda tu visita técnica
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="coverage__map reveal-right">
        <iframe class="coverage__frame" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d798957.1170534918!2d-72.0!3d-34.4!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x9666324159c370ab%3A0x6fc2db5f06de5c59!2sRegi%C3%B3n%20del%20Libertador%20General%20Bernardo%20O&#39;Higgins!5e0!3m2!1ses-419!2scl!4v1" allowfullscreen loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade" title="Mapa de cobertura Región de O'Higgins"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coverage__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .coverage__info h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coverage__info h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-700), var(--blue-700));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .coverage__info p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coverage__list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .coverage__list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .coverage__list li i {
    color: var(--blue-700);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .coverage__map {
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    position: relative;
  }

  .coverage__map::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0 rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.1);
    transition: box-shadow 0.6s ease;
  }

  .coverage__map:hover::before {
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 80px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.08);
  }

  .coverage__frame {
    width: 100%;
    height: 300px;
    display: block;
    border: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 868px) {
    .coverage__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .coverage__frame {
      height: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
